<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1218] Implement in-memory column</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1218</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;HCD already talks of in-memory columns; its just not implemented.  With hfile this should now be possible &amp;#8211; if set, read in the whole storefile and serve from the blockbuffer.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12415531">HBASE-1218</key>
            <summary>Implement in-memory column</summary>
